Package me.paul.hw3.simulation

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Agent<T extends Agent<T>>
    Class represents an Agent that exists and live on the Board grid environment
    Coyote
    An implementation of Agent in the form of a predator living in the Simulation
    RoadRunner
    An implementation of Agent in the form of a prey living in the Simulation
    Simulation
    A simple 2-dimensional predator-prey Simulation on a bounded row x column grid.
    SimulationBuilder
    Simple Singleton design which is used to create instances of a Simulation
